{"analytics_identifier":"PB1465","base_path":"/government/organisations/building-safety-regulator","content_id":"cc6cdcfe-7756-4737-bd88-1199c8e6bb8f","description":"We regulate higher-risk buildings and work to raise safety standards for England’s buildings and improve built environment competence across England and Wales. BSR is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government .","details":{"acronym":"BSR","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>We regulate higher-risk buildings and work to raise safety standards for England’s buildings and improve built environment competence across England and Wales.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Building Safety Regulator\">BSR</abbr> is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/ministry-of-housing-communities-local-government\">Ministry of Housing, Communities and Local Government</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"ministry-of-housing-communities-local-government","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"custom","formatted_title":"Building<br/>Safety<br/>Regulator","image":{"alt_text":"Building Safety Regulator","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69667da0e8c04eb2919f7737/BSR-logo-300w.png"}},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"News story","href":"/government/news/bsr-plans-to-reduce-external-remediation-delays-and-improve-management-of-application-caseloads","image":{"alt_text":"2 people in hard hats surveying a high-rise building","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d619643efd329a5269df4b/s712_2_people_in_hard_hats_surveying_a_higher-risk_building.png","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d61964e99da92a6369df41/s465_2_people_in_hard_hats_surveying_a_higher-risk_building.png","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69d