 leadership, and takes particular responsibility for the borders, immigration and citizenship system.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2018-10-08T08:07:01Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Second Permanent Secretary","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-04-06T15:45:16Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Tricia Hayes CB - Second Permanent Secretary","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"c246929c-a1c8-4ed2-901a-a0e567dffbd5","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2021-07-04T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":6743,"started_on":"2021-04-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"c5cef26e-c0eb-4f1c-b926-9b5f1a3f0870","details":{"body":"<p>The Director General  is responsible for:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>leading on developing, co-ordinating and delivering the government’s strategy, policy and legislation on crime, policing, fire, international law enforcement and judicial cooperation</li>\n  <li>creating the Emergency Services Network, a 4G digital critical communications network which will transform how Britain’s emergency and rescue services operate, and leading various other national digital law enforcement programmes</li>\n  <li>leading the policy and operational teams working on modern slavery and human trafficking, including the UK’s National Referral Mechanism and provision of support for victims in England and Wales</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The DG also serves as a member of the Home Office Executive Committee.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-04-16T14:30:37Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director General, Public Safety Group","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-07-05T09:46:07Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Tricia Hayes CB - Director General, Public Safety Group","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"4dbc201d-de5b-4701-a8e0-33f33ef11e6c","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2021-03-31T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":6115,"started_on":"2020-02-24T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"846a4bb8-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The group’s core mission is to keep citizens safe, cut crime, protect the vulnerable and reform police, fire and rescue services to improve their efficiency and effectiveness.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2016-05-03T08:49:31Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director General, Crime, Policing and Fire Group","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-04-01T10:30:57Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Tricia Hayes - Director General, Crime, Policing and Fire Group","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"cc6a8297-d042-4c33-8e34-e62b6465b663","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2020-02-23T00:00:00+00:00","person_appointment_order":3296,"started_on":"2016-04-01T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"f90580a8-325d-4a0a-9b29-2279767ba622","details":{"body":"<p>To contribute to the collective leadership of  the Department for Transport (<abbr title=\"Department for Transport\">DfT</abbr> ) as a Board and Executive Committee member and lead the Roads Transport Group. The main areas of responsibility are: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>ensuring the department’s resources and plans align with our business plan</li>\n  <li>development of policy in relation to roads, motoring, road and vehicle safety, vehicle autonomy, vehicle decarbonisation, traffic, sustainable travel, logistics, supply chains and the border</li>\n  <li>managing the government funding of, and relationship with, Transport for London</li>\n  <li>client management of National Highways and its Roads Investment programme</li>\n  <li>sponsorship of  <abbr title=\"Department for Transport\">DfT</abbr>’s motoring agencies (<abbr title=\"Vehicle Certification Agency\">VCA</abbr>, <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr> and <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>)</li>\n  <li>sponsorship of Active Travel England, an agency of the <abbr title=\"Department for Transport\">DfT</abbr>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-04-08T13:42:59Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Director General Road Transport Group","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2020-03-02T14:35:05Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Tricia Hayes - Director General for Roads, Places and Environment Group","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-03-11T11:24:57Z","schema_name":"person","title":"Tricia Hayes CB","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/people/tricia-hayes","withdrawn":false},{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/kemi-oguntoye","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/kemi-oguntoye","base_path":"/government/people/kemi-oguntoye","content_id":"d8c84776-bfca-4694-b6d8-21bbe684ed95","details":{"image":{"url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69b1534bcdd628b29e349614/s465_Kemi_Oguntoye.png"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"1954b5f3-15aa-439d-981d-048dbd888473","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":1,"started_on":"2026-01-27T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"7cb87f25-28a9-4245-b566-13e692b031cf","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-03-11T12:23:11Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Non-Executive Director","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2026-03-11T12:23:41Z","schema_name":"role_appointment